crystalgl: crystalgl (Next-gen crystal (KDE) window decoration)
crystalgl:
crystalgl: Crystal-GL is the next generation of the crystal window decoration
crystalgl: theme. By using OpenGL to render itself, it simulates refraction
crystalgl: and light mapping!
crystalgl: It looks very similar to crystal, but has more eye-candy and smooth
crystalgl: animations.
